it'll be great.

253
00:12:46,533 --> 00:12:48,342
To be totally honest,

254
00:12:48,467 --> 00:12:51,269
you were the last person
I wanted by my side for this.

255
00:12:52,868 --> 00:12:54,856
But I'm actually glad you're here.

256
00:12:56,891 --> 00:12:57,676
Good.

257
00:12:57,801 --> 00:12:59,743
Now, will you get
your butt out there

258
