being a diva for once?

259
00:13:01,834 --> 00:13:03,365
Please, can you?

260
00:13:03,601 --> 00:13:05,001
Think bitch.

261
00:13:05,285 --> 00:13:06,742
Attitude, attitude.

262
00:13:06,912 --> 00:13:08,536
Shake it off. Breathe.

263
00:13:08,767 --> 00:13:10,747
Work the ladies, work the
ladies, work the ladies.

264
00:13:10,915 --> 00:13:11,748
Let's go.

265
00:13:20,675 --> 00:13:23,218
Man, if they ever found out
I was selling these treasure maps...

266
00:13:23,386 --> 00:13:24,774
Yeah, mum's the word.

267
00:13:26,242 --> 00:13:27,764
Where are the security codes?

268
00:13:28,891 --> 00:13:31,434
- You're doing the world a favor.
