274
00:13:47,584 --> 00:13:49,952
So, we make the lead a woman.

275
00:13:50,133 --> 00:13:52,788
I'm telling you, Cameron Diaz
is going to flip for this thing.

276
00:13:52,968 --> 00:13:55,124
We tell the story in
chronological order,

277
00:13:55,300 --> 00:13:56,667
