278
00:13:56,837 --> 00:13:58,335
How's that sound?

279
00:13:58,505 --> 00:14:00,376
Andrew Misher's office...

280
00:14:01,615 --> 00:14:03,925
it sounds very different.

281
00:14:04,303 --> 00:14:06,385
Great. Listen, I got to head out,

282
00:14:06,567 --> 00:14:07,678
but I love

283
00:14:07,848 --> 00:14:08,743
what we're orbiting here.

284
00:14:08,868 --> 00:14:10,367
Can't wait for your new take.

285
00:14:11,334 --> 00:14:12,476
We'll talk soon, kid.

286
00:14:20,434 --> 00:14:23,527
Andrew Misher's office...

287
00:14:23,697 --> 00:14:24,942
I know that look.

288
00:14:25,199 --> 00:14:26,655
You think you're giving
Andrew Misher Sling Blade,

289
00:14:26,825 --> 00:14:29,617
and he pitches you back
the next Freddy Krueger.

290
00:14:29,787 --> 00:14:31,442
Oh, no, it wasn't so bad.

291
00:14:31,622 --> 00:14:33,109
Right.

292
00:14:33,290 --> 00:14:34,914
