293
00:14:35,084 --> 00:14:37,843
Sorry I missed your meeting. I had a
five-minute notes call with Michael Bay

294
00:14:38,045 --> 00:14:39,609
that turned into two
hours of arguing.

295
00:14:39,734 --> 00:14:41,045
Geez.

296
00:14:43,759 --> 00:14:44,743
Miller, I know. I'm the one

297
00:14:44,868 --> 00:14:46,409
Charlie Kitsis called
to get you in the door.

298
00:14:46,595 --> 00:14:49,763
