to make that happen...

311
00:15:19,878 --> 00:15:21,419
on your terms.

312
00:15:22,567 --> 00:15:23,576
Are you punking me?

313
00:15:23,799 --> 00:15:26,209
Is it, like...

314
00:15:26,334 --> 00:15:27,717
Seriously?

315
00:15:32,641 --> 00:15:33,676
So, what's taking her

316
00:15:33,851 --> 00:15:35,558
