Okay, so here's the deal.

317
00:15:35,728 --> 00:15:37,809
Riley's chest has
seen the light of day

318
00:15:37,980 --> 00:15:39,603
about as often
as the latest Usher album.

319
00:15:39,773 --> 00:15:42,309
She's been with...
three guys her entire life,

320
00:15:42,526 --> 00:15:45,109
and her idea of a good time
is hanging out at Whole Foods

321
00:15:45,300 --> 00:15:46,569
trying to convince you

322
00:15:46,767 --> 00:15:48,779
to save the whales.

323
00:15:48,949 --> 00:15:50,442
So, if you want her
to feel comfortable,

324
00:15:50,617 --> 00:15:52,376
you're going to have to appeal
to her sensibilities.

325
00:15:52,578 --> 00:15:54,467
Comfortable is the last thing
I want her to feel.

326
00:15:56,267 --> 00:15:57,746
All right. You ready?

327
00:15:57,916 --> 00:15:59,039
You good to lose the shirt?

328
00:15:59,209 --> 00:16:00,676
"Good" is stretching it.

329
00:16:00,801 --> 00:16:01,975
Come on, sweetie.

330
00:16:02,171 --> 00:16:05,209
Riley, this is a jeans ad, you know.
All the models are topless,

331
00:16:05,334 --> 00:16:07,923
