so just relax...

332
00:16:08,100 --> 00:16:10,450
deep breath.
It'll be beautiful.

333
00:16:13,234 --> 00:16:14,567
Here we go.

334
00:16:16,894 --> 00:16:18,684
There we go. Don't be afraid

335
00:16:18,854 --> 00:16:20,769
