336
00:16:21,023 --> 00:16:23,439
No more fake smiles.
We tried that already.

337
00:16:23,650 --> 00:16:24,773
Come on, this is a campaign

338
00:16:24,985 --> 00:16:26,025
about raw emotion.

339
00:16:26,195 --> 00:16:27,818
You're a real woman
with real feelings.

340
00:16:28,197 --> 00:16:29,942
Let it all out.
What do you think

341
00:16:30,115 --> 00:16:31,142
I'm trying to do?
I don't know.

342
00:16:31,325 --> 00:16:33,115
You're still hiding it. Come on.

343
00:16:33,327 --> 00:16:35,117
These are the jeans
that the teacher puts on

344
00:16:35,287 --> 00:16:36,327
