00:21:37,300 --> 00:21:39,934
I would have remembered you.

464
00:21:42,667 --> 00:21:45,242
You know, I'm having
drinks tonight at Katsuya

465
00:21:45,367 --> 00:21:46,442
with the VP of Paramount.

466
00:21:46,567 --> 00:21:48,776
We'll probably be done by 10:00.

467
00:21:48,901 --> 00:21:50,433
You want to join me after?

468
00:21:50,767 --> 00:21:53,061
Uh, meet you after your drinks?

469
00:21:53,400 --> 00:21:54,520
To work on our pitch.

470
00:21:57,501 --> 00:21:59,025
T... to work on the pitch.

471
00:21:59,334 --> 00:22:01,942
Sounds good, sounds...
yeah, sounds great.

472
00:22:02,067 --> 00:22:05,267
I'll save you a seat at the bar.

