476
00:22:25,595 --> 00:22:27,042
I'm actually just on my way out.

477
00:22:27,264 --> 00:22:29,576
Yeah, so what's with
the black gloves?

478
00:22:29,766 --> 00:22:31,109
Lauren, this isn't a good time.
Right.

479
00:22:31,234 --> 00:22:32,875
First you get beaten up,
then the blueprints.

