00:22:44,701 --> 00:22:48,109
Lauren, get in the car.

484
00:22:48,285 --> 00:22:49,975
We got to get out of here.

485
00:22:50,162 --> 00:22:51,244
Now.

486
00:22:54,958 --> 00:22:58,743
Guess there's no love lost
between you and the speed limit.

